Package trees.building Description

Package collecting supporting classes. It is only meant for internal use (although they are usable outside, too).

Classes for extracting the tree structure of a given object net. The structure is converted into an equivalent tree structure which can be used for the layout algorithm. The extraction can be controlled with the help of the annotations @Ignore, @Nodes, and @Label.

Author:
Marcus Deininger
